      <div class="sb-panel-img">
        {% if section.settings.panel_bridge_image != blank %}
          <img src="{{ section.settings.panel_bridge_image | image_url: width: 700 }}" width="700" height="525" alt="Multilingual professional with SafeBuds" loading="lazy"/>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="r">
        <span class="panel-eyebrow">The Multilingual Professional</span>
        <h3>Mumbai meeting. Tokyo client. Zero awkward pauses.</h3>
        <p class="sb-panel-scene">Hyderabad IT consultant. Client in Osaka, supplier in Shenzhen, manager in Dubai. Four people. Four languages. Used to mean an interpreter or Google Translate held up to a phone. Not anymore.</p>
        <p class="sb-panel-body">SphereLingo™ translates a live conversation into your language as it's happening — directly into your ear. Whether you're an NRI dealing with family paperwork, a Delhi exporter on a Chinese supplier call, or a Bangalore startup on a US investor call, the language gap closes before it opens.</p>
