    <!-- Entertainment -->
    <div id="sb-p-entertain" class="sb-panel">
      <div class="sb-panel-img">
        {% if section.settings.panel_entertain_image != blank %}
          <img src="{{ section.settings.panel_entertain_image | image_url: width: 700 }}" width="700" height="525" alt="Entertainment with SafeBuds" loading="lazy"/>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="r">
        <span class="panel-eyebrow">The Entertainment Audience</span>
        <h3>Netflix chal raha hai. Ghar mein sab ko pata bhi nahi chalega.</h3>
        <p class="sb-panel-scene">Friday night. Sacred Games cue. Dark room. SafeBuds on, volume up. The doorbell rang — you heard it. That's the point. No more missed knocks, no more "ek second" panic.</p>
        <p class="sb-panel-body">Most earphones force a trade-off: full audio or full awareness. SafeBuds gives you both. Deep immersion in Mirzapur or a midnight BGMI session — while still hearing your phone buzz, your mom call, or your delivery boy at the door. You never have to pull one out.</p>
        <div class="sb-panel-pts">
          <div class="sb-pt"><div class="sb-pt-dot"></div><span>Custom EQ via WeHear app — deep bass for movies, clarity for dialogue</span></div>
          <div class="sb-pt"><div class="sb-pt-dot"></div><span>9g open fit — wear for 4-hour binge sessions, no ear fatigue</span></div>
          <div class="sb-pt"><div class="sb-pt-dot"></div><span>Stay aware — hear the room while staying in the scene</span></div>
          <div class="sb-pt"><div class="sb-pt-dot"></div><span>Bluetooth 5.4 — instant pair to phone, laptop, iPad, or TV</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Parent -->
    <div id="sb-p-parent" class="sb-panel">
      <div class="sb-panel-img">
        {% if section.settings.panel_parent_image != blank %}
          <img src="{{ section.settings.panel_parent_image | image_url: width: 700 }}" width="700" height="525" alt="Parent choosing SafeBuds for their child" loading="lazy"/>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="r">
        <span class="panel-eyebrow">The Aware Parent</span>
        <h3>JEE prep. 8 hours a day. Earphones in. This is the one you give them.</h3>
        <p class="sb-panel-scene">Your daughter has been studying since morning — Unacademy, YouTube, then calls with her study group. Same in-ear earphones since Class 9. You've read what prolonged canal use does. SafeBuds is the decision you make before it's too late to make it.</p>
        <p class="sb-panel-body">The WHO estimates 1.1 billion young people globally are at risk from recreational audio use. In India, with marathon coaching sessions and screen-heavy lifestyles, the exposure is especially high. SafeBuds rests outside the ear canal entirely. Nothing goes in. No pressure, no heat, no bacteria — and they still hear you when you call them for dinner.</p>
        <div class="sb-panel-pts">
