          <div class="sb-pt"><div class="sb-pt-dot"></div><span>ENT doctor certified safe for all-day daily use</span></div>
          <div class="sb-pt"><div class="sb-pt-dot"></div><span>9g light — comfortable for 6-hour study and class sessions</span></div>
          <div class="sb-pt"><div class="sb-pt-dot"></div><span>They still hear ambient sound — safer, more aware at all times</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
